<span id="freeTextContainer5957641771672732942">Glad I read recommendation from an online professor. This was the American Holocaust. The raw description of the atrocities the indigenous people suffered gives a person context as why American society is in it&apos;s current state of upheaval.</span>
  <span id="freeText5957641771672732942" style="display:none">Glad I read recommendation from an online professor. This was the American Holocaust. The raw description of the atrocities the indigenous people suffered gives a person context as why American society is in it's current state of upheaval.</span>
